---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="About Me - Design for the Continuum" activePage="abstract">
  <!-- Title Section -->
  <section class="px-6 lg:px-24 py-12 lg:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-[1100px]">
      <h1 class="font-black text-3xl lg:text-[50px] leading-[1.15] mb-12">
        why me why now
      </h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <section class="px-6 lg:px-24 py-8 lg:py-12">
    <div class="max-w-[1000px] lg:ml-[200px]">
      <!-- First Paragraph -->
      <p
        class="text-xl lg:text-[32px] leading-[1.2] font-semibold mb-12 lg:mb-16"
      >
        The PhD in Art, Design and Transdisciplinarity at IED Turin is an
        experimental space where I can carry forward this research. I've begun
        to explore it and to hybridize it with various teachers, mentors,
        advisors, and fellow curious minds.
      </p>

      <!-- Second Paragraph -->
      <p
        class="text-xl lg:text-[32px] leading-[1.2] font-semibold mb-12 lg:mb-16"
      >
        I need practices of enchantment and liberation, and I know these can
        help me manifest a new relationship with what surrounds me. This
        exploration lies at the foundation of a new paradigm that goes beyond
        the threshold of what we can imagine today.
      </p>

      <!-- Acknowledgments -->
      <div
        class="mt-16 lg:mt-20 pt-8 border-t-2 border-charcoal/20 mb-12 lg:mb-16"
      >
        <p class="text-base lg:text-[20px] font-semibold opacity-70">
          I thank Marta, Hanna Maria, Barbara, Gaetano, Neha, Attilio.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Images Section -->
      <div class="space-y-8 lg:space-y-12 mt-16 lg:mt-20">
        <!-- First Image -->
        <div>
          <img
            src="/assets/1.jpg"
            alt="A contemplative scene of a concrete pier extending into calm water with a glowing architectural structure"
            class="w-full h-auto object-cover"
          />
        </div>

        <!-- Second Image -->
        <div>
          <img
            src="/assets/2.jpg"
            alt="Hands reaching through swirling water, symbolizing immersion and exploration"
            class="w-full h-auto object-cover"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
